53-124.01.Fees for annual licenses.

(1) The fees for annual licenses finally issued by the commission shall be as provided in this section and section 53-124.

(2) Airline license ... $100

(3) Boat license ... $50

(4) Bottle club license ... $300

(5) Special party bus license ... $75

(6) Manufacturer's license:

ClassFee - In DollarsAlcohol and spirits1,000Beer - tier one100Beer - tier two200Beer - tier three350Beer - tier four500Beer - tier five650Beer - tier six700Beer - tier seven800Wine250

(11) Retail license:

(13) Wholesale license:

SourceLaws 2010, LB861, § 57;Laws 2013, LB230, § 3;Laws 2015, LB330, § 17;Laws 2016, LB1105, § 16;Laws 2018, LB1120, § 12;Laws 2020, LB734, § 8;Laws 2025, LB478, § 5.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
